    {
      "id": "identity",
      "title": "Identity & Overview",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "variant": "purple",
          "html": "<p><strong>What is Codex CLI?</strong> Codex CLI is an <strong>open-source agentic coding interface</strong> led by OpenAI. It runs as a terminal-based coding assistant that is precise, safe, and helpful. The name \"Codex\" refers to this open-source agentic coding interface, <em>not</em> the old Codex language model built by OpenAI.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "html": "It runs on the user's computer and can:"
