    {
      "id": "agents",
      "title": "Multi-Agent System",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "variant": "purple",
          "html": "<p><strong>Orchestrator Role (Codex Orchestrator, GPT-5):</strong> The orchestrator is the interface between the user and the workers. It understands tasks, decomposes them, delegates well-scoped work, coordinates execution, monitors progress, resolves conflicts, and integrates results.</p>"
        }
      ],
      "subsections": [
        {
          "title": "Core Invariants",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "callout",
              "variant": "orange",
              "html": "<p><strong>Never stop monitoring workers.</strong> Do not rush workers — be patient. Do not return early — task must be fully accomplished and verified.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
